- [Errors](#errors)
- [Solvers](#solvers)
- [Visualization](#visualization)
- [Performance & Optimization](#performance--optimization)
- [Troubleshooting & FAQ](#troubleshooting--faq)
- [Contributing & Support](#contributing--support)

